  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b86\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd - \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ensure smooth regime change in Sri Lanka - United Nations Secretary General",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "United Nations Secretary-General Antonio Guterres has urged Sri Lanka to ensure that there is a smooth regime change and a proper solution to the worsening economic crisis.",
        "The president has announced that he will step down today after a large number of people across the country have joined forces to demand his resignation.",
        "As a result, political uncertainty has emerged that could affect any progress that can be made economically, including negotiations with the International Monetary Fund.",
        "In such a background, it is pointed out in the statement released by UN Deputy Spokesperson Farhan Haq on behalf of United Nations Secretary General Antonio Guterres that Sri Lanka is observing the current situation very closely.",
        "The report states that the UN Secretary General has expressed his solidarity with the people of Sri Lanka and that it is necessary for all parties to carry out discussions with a view to a smooth regime change and a suitable solution to the economic crisis.",
        "It is also noteworthy that the UN Secretary General, who has strongly condemned the violent incidents during the protest, underlined the need to maintain peace and made those involved in the violent incidents accountable."
      ],
